      "rdf:value": "<L>6923<pc>0429-b<k1>Dan<k2>Dan\r\n1. {#Dan#}¦ {%DHAN%} (<ab>cf.</ab> {%dhanv%}), <ab>f.</ab> †,\r\n<ab>Par.</ab> {@1.@} To put in motion (<ab>ved.</ab>). {@2.@} †\r\nTo bear or produce grains, etc. <ab>Caus.</ab>\r\n{%dhanaya,%} To put in motion, <ls>Chr.</ls> 293,\r\n3 = <ls>Rigv.</ls> i. 88, 3.\r\n<LEND>"
